triageapp.components

Class ERAdmin

  • java.lang.Object
    • triageapp.components.ERAdmin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ERAdmin
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The class that handles all high level operations in TriangeApp. Handles: adding Patient adding Prescription adding Vital Signs sending Patient to doctor looking up a Patient signing in Patient closing Visit Record loading lists
    See Also:

      • closeCase

        public void closeCase(Patient patient,
             TriageDBAdapter dbAdapter)
        Closes a Patient's current ERVisit. Removes references of the patient in urgencyList and patientsSentToDoctor. Updates the ERVisit entry in the database.
        Parameters:
        patient - The Patient whose ERVisit is being closed.
        dbAdapter - The database adapter (helper).

      • signInPatient

        public Patient signInPatient(String healthNumber,
                    TriageDBAdapter dbAdapter)
        Signs in an existing Patient. Creates a new ERVisit for the Patient and add a corresponding entry in the database.
        Parameters:
        healthNumber - The Patient's health card number.
        dbAdapter - The database adapter (helper).
        Returns:
        The Patient being signed in.
